The script “main.py” is aimed at creating a “requirements.txt” for Python projects. This requirements file contains the installed package versions used on a particular python project. So another user can test or use your project, after installing the aforementioned python packages.

Instructions of use in the script itself.

Enjoy, and feel free to improve this project!